listing_info_description: Let the oceanfront property and private beach take your breath away! One of the very few 4.5-star cottages on PEI. This stunning rental will not disappoint. This property is steps to the ocean glass waters, miles of beautiful shorelines for barefoot beachcombing! This breathtaking magical place has some of the best sunsets! Over and above your own private beach, you are also within a two-minute drive of Cabot Beach Provincial Park. You are a close 10-minute drive to the village of Kensington.
